Features:
    real time Progress Tracking for parents and teachers.
    AI algorithm for learning the learning style of every individual and storing them in a separate row for each child in the database.
    The AI algorithm will use the learned style of the individual to give personally catered recommendations for the learning of the child.
    Different and innovative ways of learning for students.(games, videos, quizes, storytelling)
    make content engaging as students with adhd suffer from lack of focus. they are hyperactive.
    reward system.
    1-1 sessions with teachers.(subscribe)
    meditation and focus related activities.
    Get age and disability of the student at the start when opening the website for the first time and give the content based on those parameters.
    If the child has no disabilities, then the default homepage will suffice.



